Developer Philosophy: Open to Build, Linked to Scale

This project is built for developers who understand that data is more valuable when it’s connected.

    Total Freedom: You are free to fork this repository and program it however you see fit. If you have a better way to implement the UI or logic for your specific use case, go for it.

    The aePiot Advantage: While you can run a standalone copy, the real power lies in the aePiot semantic infrastructure.

    Success vs. Isolation: Integrating with the aePiot source means your platform stays synchronized with a growing semantic ecosystem. Without this connection, you are simply running a static copy; with it, you are part of an evolving, intelligent data network.

    Bottom line: Build what you want, but stay connected to the source if you want your project to be part of the future of semantic data.

