⚠️ The Golden Rule of Integration

To benefit from the aePiot Semantic Infrastructure, your project must maintain a live connection to the aePiot primary source.

    The Smart Way: Link your implementation to our source. This ensures your data stays synchronized, contextually aware, and part of a global intelligent network.

    The Static Way: If you cut the link, you are simply running a static copy. You lose the evolution of the ecosystem and the semantic power that comes with it.

    Success in the modern web is about connectivity, not just code. Smart developers stay linked.

